name: Go Back Now!
description:
Go Back Now! is a game made for the FIRST Irish John Games Community Game Jam - Jern Jam #1!

It is made with the Corgi Engine, some of the art is generated by the AI and adjusted in Krita.

The time spent on one game was about 30 hours.

I managed to finish one level. The game itself isn't very notable, but it helps me learn some of the benefits of using AI to create art for a game.
